 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75adb78a3f214622626bbb9cce86422623cc8515","tid":661803,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a663bbf795dd6702541e36be1621d6821f4bd91","tid":661803,"uid":104699,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"英國就精英主義，醫生要負最大責任。香港就科舉主義，醫生要負責收最高人工，但唔洗負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"支持入返英聯邦醫生，地獄鬼國嗰啲就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964a2fa97c8189b2086eb467b5d72030ac53e40d","tid":661803,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d4bd8b8cd991d087690c2cc6d58a2ff9d43485","tid":661803,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"193b325037cb53f6f28b220bf15f43e4093ce8e3","tid":661803,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2d4bd8b8cd991d087690c2cc6d58a2ff9d43485","tid":661803,"uid":29702,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:12:49.000Z","msg":"又係足絲雞你呢個DC9呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d96839c503709bb6e8fc8d33e0c59c8f7e15a16","tid":661803,"uid":123308,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"醫生一定唔會有錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，錯的都只是其他醫護人員 <br />\n醫生讀咁多書，做任何嘢一定係啱的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其他人唔可以批評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有如要評論球員，就先要做到費爵爺 level，踢波踢到專業球員水平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要講馬，你就要先做過騎馬師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔係醫生，就唔可以 judge 醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本土醫學院醫生獨大專政，圍內傾掂數，能夠做到高效、進步、無私，<br />\n係一班專業團結隊伍，如同警察一樣，係對病人好好的慈母嚟的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巡八次房</span>都發現唔到問題，<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">純屬不幸，於醫生無關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></ins><br />\n你唔明白只係因為你讀得唔夠多書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6211131e30496b24f8e186fc6236f930074f5a0b","tid":661803,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aba60d14589a431873800fa9d2ca382a30b268b1","tid":661803,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75adb78a3f214622626bbb9cce86422623cc8515","tid":661803,"uid":16846,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a663bbf795dd6702541e36be1621d6821f4bd91","tid":661803,"uid":104699,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"英國就精英主義，醫生要負最大責任。香港就科舉主義，醫生要負責收最高人工，但唔洗負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"支持入返英聯邦醫生，地獄鬼國嗰啲就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T09:29:58.000Z","msg":"你死啦你，想引入英美醫生打爛本土醫生一界專政個飯碗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想顛覆醫學權威專業？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b59e1d6d99fb2871ff3265c32e747fce64ed53","tid":66180